OH, MY GOD. OH, MY GOD.

90
00:03:42,639 --> 00:03:45,141
OH, HONEY, HOLD ON.

91
00:03:45,141 --> 00:03:48,277
DON'T LET GO!
DON'T LET GO! PLEASE, GET ME UP!

92
00:03:48,278 --> 00:03:49,529
HOLD ON.

93
00:03:50,146 --> 00:03:51,397
HOLD ON.

94
00:03:51,397 --> 00:03:53,899
