BUT I THINK I GOT DOWN,
ONCE I GOT MOVING,

345
00:20:20,485 --> 00:20:22,353
IN ABOUT 2 SECONDS FLAT.

346
00:20:22,988 --> 00:20:24,856
DO I GET POINTS
FOR THAT?

347
00:20:24,856 --> 00:20:27,358
NO ONE'S
KEEPING SCORE HERE.

348
00:20:27,359 --> 00:20:31,112
