I'M FAILING.

349
00:20:31,113 --> 00:20:33,615
ALL OF A SUDDEN, WHEN
I'M IN A HIGH PLACE,

350
00:20:33,615 --> 00:20:35,500
I FEEL THE DROP
PULLING ON ME,

351
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:36,751
AND ALL I CAN
THINK ABOUT IS FALLING.

352
00:20:36,752 --> 00:20:38,620
YOU WANT TO JUMP.

353
00:20:40,505 --> 00:20:43,007
YOU DON'T WASTE
ANY TIME, DO YOU?

354
00:20:43,008 --> 00:20:44,876
LIFE IS SHORT,

355
00:20:44,876 --> 00:20:48,012
AND YOUR CASE IS NOT
THAT UNIQUE, BELIEVE ME.

356
00:20:48,013 --> 00:20:52,934
I WOULD SUGGEST YOUR ACROPHOBIA
IS TRIGGERED BY ASSOCIATIONS

357
00:20:52,935 --> 00:20:54,186
REMINDFUL OF YOUR
SISTER'S DEATH.

358
00:20:54,803 --> 00:20:56,688
NOW, HEIGHT WILL ALWAYS BE
THE STRONGEST ASSOCIATION,

359
00:20:56,688 --> 00:20:59,190
BUT ANY ASSOCIATION--
SIGHTS, SMELLS, SOUNDS--

360
00:20:59,191 --> 00:21:00,442
HAVE THE POTENTIAL

361
00:21:00,442 --> 00:21:03,561
TO PUT YOU ON THE BRINK,

362
00:21:03,562 --> 00:21:06,014
WHICH IS THE CLASSIC PLACE
FOR THE ACROPHOBIC--

363
00:21:06,014 --> 00:21:09,734
TO FALL, TO JUMP,
TO BE OR NOT TO BE.

364
00:21:10,369 --> 00:21:12,871
I GOT TO GET PAST THIS.

365
00:21:12,871 --> 00:21:14,739
I CAN'T LIVE
LIKE THIS.

366
00:21:14,740 --> 00:21:17,876
IT'S AFFECTING
MY MARRIAGE, MY WORK, MY SLEEP.

367
00:21:17,876 --> 00:21:20,995
I'LL PUT YOU IN TOUCH
WITH A NUMBER OF GOOD THERAPISTS

368
00:21:20,996 --> 00:21:22,247
THAT WILL HELP YOU
WITH RELAXATION, HYPNOSIS--

369
00:21:22,247 --> 00:21:24,749
NO. I WANT
TO WORK WITH YOU.

370
00:21:24,750 --> 00:21:27,252
NO, I'M A RESEARCHER, CARLA.

371
00:21:27,252 --> 00:21:31,005
