373
00:21:36,011 --> 00:21:39,764
WELL, UM, I'M WORKING
WITH ONLY 4 PATIENTS.

374
00:21:41,016 --> 00:21:42,267
IT'S COMPLETELY
EXPERIMENTAL.

375
00:21:43,518 --> 00:21:46,020
AND THEY'RE ALL
EXTREME CASES.

376
00:21:46,021 --> 00:21:49,157
YOU KNOW WHAT I THINK?

377
00:21:49,157 --> 00:21:51,025
I THINK YOU'RE
GOING TO BE FINE.

378
00:21:51,026 --> 00:21:54,779
I THINK YOU'RE GOING
TO MAKE PEACE WITH THIS.

379
00:21:56,031 --> 00:21:57,916
I GOT TO GO. OK?

380
00:21:58,533 --> 00:21:59,784
THANKS FOR YOUR TIME.

381
00:21:59,785 --> 00:22:01,670
YOU'RE WELCOME.

382
00:22:17,886 --> 00:22:19,137
I CAN DO THIS.

