414
00:25:12,160 --> 00:25:14,045
YEAH, YOU'RE TELLING ME.

415
00:25:14,045 --> 00:25:17,164
LISTEN, SHE'S BEEN SEDATED,
SO KEEP IT SIMPLE.

416
00:25:30,929 --> 00:25:32,814
I DON'T KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.

417
00:25:32,814 --> 00:25:35,933
