WE SHOULD GO SEE DR. SADOWSKI AGAIN.

428
00:26:05,347 --> 00:26:07,215
OH, MARK, HE DOESN'T
WANT TO TAKE ANY PATIENTS.

429
00:26:07,849 --> 00:26:09,717
