433
00:26:17,859 --> 00:26:19,110
OK?

434
00:26:19,110 --> 00:26:20,361
MM-HMM.

435
00:26:20,362 --> 00:26:24,115
LET'S GET YOU
OUT OF HERE, ALL RIGHT? OK.

436
00:26:24,733 --> 00:26:25,984
I TRIED TO JUMP OFF
THE FIFTH STORY OF A PARKING GARAGE.

437
00:26:25,984 --> 00:26:27,869
WHAT MORE DOES IT TAKE?

438
00:26:27,869 --> 00:26:29,120
