OF SOMETHING YOU DON'T COMPREHEND.

439
00:26:29,738 --> 00:26:31,623
YOU THINK THIS IS ARMY
BOOT CAMP.

440
00:26:31,623 --> 00:26:34,125
WHAT I DO IS NAVY SEAL
STUFF, GET IT?

441
00:26:34,743 --> 00:26:36,628
I'M WORKING ON A TECHNIQUE
CALLED "FLOODING."

442
00:26:37,245 --> 00:26:40,381
IT PUTS THE SUBJECTS
IN UNRELIEVED CONFRONTATION WITH THEIR PHOBIAS.

443
00:26:40,382 --> 00:26:43,501
NOW, THE THEORY
IS THAT THIS WILL ALLOW A BREAKTHROUGH,

444
00:26:43,501 --> 00:26:44,752
BUT THERE'S NO
GUARANTEE OF THAT.

445
00:26:44,753 --> 00:26:46,004
JUST AS LIKELY,
THEY'LL CRASH AND BURN.

446
00:26:46,638 --> 00:26:49,140
IT'S FOR CASES THAT HAVE
NO OTHER HOPE OF RECOVERY.

447
00:26:49,140 --> 00:26:51,008
WELL, OK, THEN LET'S--

448
00:26:51,009 --> 00:26:52,260
NO, BUT DO YOU THINK
IT'LL WORK?

449
00:26:52,260 --> 00:26:54,762
WELL, IT ALREADY HAS WORKED
IN PRELIMINARY TESTS.

450
00:26:55,397 --> 00:26:57,265
BUT I'M TRYING TO ANSWER
A BIGGER QUESTION HERE.

451
00:26:57,265 --> 00:27:02,270
IF ACROPHOBICS IMPROVE
WHEN THEY CONQUER THEIR GENERIC FEARS--

452
00:27:02,270 --> 00:27:05,406
AIRPLANES, ELEVATORS,
ROOFTOPS--

453
00:27:05,407 --> 00:27:09,160
WHAT HAPPENS WHEN THEY
BREAK THROUGH TO THE UNDERLYING CORE TERROR?

454
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:12,163
WHAT WAS HIDDEN
IN YOUR RELATIONSHIP WITH YOUR SISTER?

455
00:27:12,163 --> 00:27:15,282
OR MORE SERIOUSLY,

456
00:27:15,283 --> 00:27:17,785
YOU WILLING TO RISK
THE POSSIBILITY...

457
00:27:21,539 --> 00:27:24,675
IS THERE ANY HISTORY
OF MENTAL ILLNESS IN YOUR FAMILY?

458
00:27:29,047 --> 00:27:30,932
UM...

459
00:27:30,932 --> 00:27:34,685
MY MOTHER SUFFERED
FROM SCHIZOPHRENIA.

460
00:27:34,686 --> 00:27:37,805
THAT'S NOT ALWAYS
HEREDITARY, THOUGH, IS IT?

461
00:27:37,806 --> 00:27:39,691
WELL, WE DON'T KNOW.

462
00:27:39,691 --> 00:27:42,193
BUT VERY OFTEN IT IS.

463
00:27:42,811 --> 00:27:45,947
LOOK, THIS RATCHETS
THE STAKES WAY UP FOR YOU AND CARLA.

464
00:27:45,947 --> 00:27:49,066
IF CARLA WERE TO ENTER
MY TREATMENT,

465
00:27:49,067 --> 00:27:54,072
SHE MIGHT BREAK THROUGH
HER ACROPHOBIA INTO CLARITY ABOUT HER SISTER,

466
00:27:54,072 --> 00:27:57,825
OR SHE MIGHT BREAK THROUGH
TO SOMETHING FAR MORE DEVASTATING.

467
00:28:01,579 --> 00:28:04,081
OK, SO IT'S...

468
00:28:04,082 --> 00:28:06,584
ME AGAINST THE BOGEYMAN.

469
00:28:06,584 --> 00:28:10,337
I'VE BEEN AFRAID OF THAT
MY WHOLE LIFE.

470
00:28:13,842 --> 00:28:14,475
I WANT TO DO IT.

471
00:28:17,595 --> 00:28:18,846
Mark: ARE YOU SURE?

